Cell[TextData[{
 "Two events are being translated through spacetime along a spacetime line. \
The proper time, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
 "\[CapitalDelta]\[Tau]"],ExpressionUUID->
  "3f180f4a-65f2-4f67-8837-3dd23eab5dcb"],
 ", along the line between the events will remain constant because of \
translational symmetry. That means we could uniformly graduate the line \
according to Euclidean distance  and elapsed time along the line will be \
proportional to the Euclidean distance. Just to emphasize our point, the \
following animation repeats the same information in a slightly different \
format."
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"462e0efa-c64c-4628-aae3-3d1109eb7208"],

